Usage: edge [OPTIONS]

These lines exercise the tricky parts of the parser.

  -f, -F, --force            two short spellings plus one long spelling
  -o FILE, --output=FILE     short option with a separate argument, plus long
  --                         end-of-options marker, must NOT be counted
  - read from standard input, must NOT be counted
  --no-arg-here              a lone long option with no short alias
